title: AMD Ryzen 5 5600X
description: The AMD Ryzen 5 5600X has 6 cores and 12 threads. Its base clock is at 3.7 GHz, its turbo clock goes up to 4.6 GHz. Its multiplier is unlocked, making it possible to overclock the processor easily.
rating: Based on 148 benchmarks we rate its gaming performance level at 7.67/10. We think it is a reasonable strong processor for current games.
